These do-it-all boxes and bowls will make your cabinets look like a dream. Collapse and stack them for space-saving organization, or fill them up while you meal prep.


Buy more for bundled savings! Your kitchen cabinets will thank you.

  • Dishwasher and microwave safe
  • Four clasp lid creates a spill-proof seal
  • Comes apart for easy cleaning
  • LFGB Platinum cured premium food grade silicone
  • BPA & BPS-free polypropylene lid, clasps, and ring (grade 5 recyclable too!)
  • 10-Pack comes with 5x Bowls & 5x Boxes
  • 12-Pack comes with 6x Bowls & 6x Boxes
  • 18-Pack comes with 9x Bowls & 9x Boxes
  • 24-Pack comes with 12x Bowls & 12x Boxes

All Stojo products are backed by our 90-day money-back guarantee.

We want you to have time to try our products, and see how they can transform your life!

Goodbye, messy cabinets!

Organized kitchen goals

Stojo will make your cabinets and counters look like a dream! No more tupperware avalanches, missing lids, and cluttered pantries. Finally, food storage organization you can be proud of.

Instant meal prep upgrade

Our food storage containers are made for your kitchen and life on the go. An instant upgrade to your meal prep, leftovers, and work lunches. Plus: they can go in the fridge, freezer, microwave, and even just on the counter.

Dishwasher & microwave safe

We make our products easy to clean so you can use them everyday! Place them on the top rack of your dishwasher, or wash by hand.

The world's safest silicone

Our food-grade silicone is LFGB Certified, which is a European safety standard that is far stricter than the FDA’s. This means you can safely use Stojo to enjoy all your favorite snacks and sammies—hot or cold.

Collapsible & convenient

Thanks to us, it’s literally never been easier (or more fun) to take snacks and meals to-go. When you’re done, fold your container up like an accordion, and close the clasps for a spill-proof seal. Now that's what we call collapsible magic!
